{"search_data": "JharkhandJharkhand Free LPG Cylinders Refill to PM Ujjwala Yojana (PMUY) Beneficiaries Jharkhand govt. to start Free LPG Cylinders Refill process to PM Ujjwala Yojana (PMUY) beneficiaries & to distribute 12 lakh new gas connections \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Jharkhand Free LPG Cylinders Refill to PMUY BeneficiariesAll the beneficiaries of the flagship Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala Yojana (PMUY) scheme in Jharkhand can now avail a free refill of their LPG cylinders. The state govt. of Jharkhand claims that this is a first-of-its-kind initiative in the country. Jharkhand govt. will start process of refill of cylinders along with distribution of 12 lakh new LPG gas connections.The process of Jhakhand Free LPG Cylinders Refill to PMUY beneficiaries will start from 23 August 2019 across the state. Jharkhand is the only state in India where beneficiaries of PMUY scheme are given free ovens and filled cylinders during distribution of LPG gas connections. Now, people can refill their cylinders for free.Since the launch of PMUY scheme in Jharkhand in 2016, around 31 lakh free LPG gas connections have already been distributed in the Jharkhand state.The PMUY scheme aims to replace the hazardous cooking fuels used in rural India with clean and efficient LPG fuel. All the families living below poverty line (BPL) are the beneficiaries of PM Ujjwala Yojana. For more details, visit the official website at https://pmuy.gov.in/  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://www.moneycontrol.com/news/economy/policy/jharkhand-pmuy-beneficiaries-to-get-free-lpg-cylinders-refill-4286551.html  at  "}